Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那竹林里休息的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一个奇怪的男人搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 您是在旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要下山的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 向西边去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着你走可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 无论如何也出不了竹林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向感相当差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经3年没人路过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很奇怪 我一直无法从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:35.34,BT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}{\an7\pos(0,0)}{\1c&H5BACA2\bord0\shad0\1a&H0}{\p1} m 95 38 l 182 41 182 480 95 480 {\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:35.34,BT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(112,74)}{\fad(1500,0)}笼\N中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实 就是山下村里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 本地人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是看不到太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不至于迷失方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 我也不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来 竹林还真大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 又兜回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 指南针并没有失效
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始是朝西走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 无意间搞错了前进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了又错 走回原处了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 不能按自己的意识前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底 怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也被困住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 暂时就在我们那里住下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就住在这里的母女俩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿现在是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来就是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是不幸中的万幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行中的人 稍微说了会儿话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妻子阿节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你陪我真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家了 你也来休息一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我再想想别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那么请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多保重?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想都觉得很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 您是从那个竹林里出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见过一个男子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被怪物困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能平安无事真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里面有白色的竹子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的丑事不要对外人说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 没能出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想看的东西 就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听村里人说这竹林里有白色的竹子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点关于你和你妻子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了那个 想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我职业范围内的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想详细了解一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是非常有趣的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定 能让你离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你 不想纠缠进来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我自己找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了这个 还有四根
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是“借间”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 请说给我听听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这竹林里发生的事情 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候在村里 听说的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个竹林里住着一对年轻夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫妇俩多年未育
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫厌倦了阴沉的家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子变得喜欢和花草说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜中常在竹林中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而某天 她对丈夫说“有孩子了”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫对妻子起了疑心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某天晚上跟踪了她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子怀抱着白色的竹子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫觉得很恶心逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被村里人劝阻又回到家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只见妻子仿佛抱小孩一样抱着竹笋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生了个竹笋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不愿意说有外遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 丈夫逃出了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我们小时候去看竹笋孩子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只看到了普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 阿节
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候她已经没了母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得她一个人好孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹和同伴们经常在这里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感觉阿节是异样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只喝水 绝对出不了竹林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家 还是接受了阿节
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过从某时开始 我们就出不了竹林了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在竹林里团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐一个个的消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识到的时候 只有我一人留在了竹林里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来 回到村里的人来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只要跟我在一起就不能离开竹林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 知道这点还把我牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我想外乡人不知道会不会有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后就在阿节家住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了妹妹以外没有别的亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的大家给我们送来吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妹妹是被村里人养大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都像家人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好村子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是日子这样持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里给的东西越来越少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜助 孤单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来 阿节怀了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起了阿节的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产婆逃回了村里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后谁也不来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你所说的借间竹是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不是竹子一类的草木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓竹子 整个竹林有着同一个根系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是一株竹子的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像世代交替的家族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借间竹侵入那根中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为家族的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从竹根中汲取养分生长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的 把竹林合成的养分馈还给竹根
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹林越扩展
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的后代也越多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的妻子是人和虫的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们虫师称之为“鬼子”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罕见的混血儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃惊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经看过女儿出生时的情形了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管父母是什么 阿节…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是阿节
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然村里人不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见过阿节就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 我们三个会去村里生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才很想出去是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 担心妹妹的境况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有因为我而受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把不自然的改变方向的地点连起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个同心圆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能按自己的意识前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在圆心的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一株吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 你们的生命之水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 说说缘由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 是很重要的水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说了 不能对外人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给喜助也喝过？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只给过 一次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是小孩子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 被村里人当成异类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我 有喜助和女儿就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然喜助出不去很可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 出不去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是 麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年又到落叶的季节了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为竹子小孩能健康长大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹子妈妈准备的竹叶饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 大家一起养大小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸一到这季节 就会想起村里的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很广阔啊 点着无数灯火 热闹的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想让你看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜助 一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 知道原因了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫和草木不一样 有自己的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给身体的各部分下达命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯彻意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这个虫而言的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以这株为中心的竹林整体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而传递意识的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个阿节她们喝的水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的水 接近这株竹也不会有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅带着这些水 就会被虫的意识影响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用说喝下去 还有在其周围的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好热 很口渴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 喝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为阿节知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:17:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 如果能从身体里抽出水分就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说实话 想不出什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能想到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我也不想这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会有别的什么影响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么终于 弄明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困住了喜助的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那东西的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它身体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像四肢是反抗不了大脑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都 听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜助 是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 喜助并不是不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜助给了不寻常的我幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却让喜助回不了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜助说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管父母是什么 我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿节
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是村子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是我 是喜助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 身体好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 那个小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我解释
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要带那种东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让我的孩子有痛苦的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说从那以后的一段日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们三人幸福地生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为借间的母株被砍的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借间竹 一株也没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从春天开始 白色竹子一株株枯萎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们是靠那水养育的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们俩很痛苦的死去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体全都 枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿节不应该那样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是阿节的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我忘记村庄的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今年也到这个季节了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色竹子 什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婴儿的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从坟墓那里传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春啸
